  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on the image above to join the Discord server.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/6daa4738e36783937b0be8ce8b84ea24.apng?t=1741346132\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/6daa4738e36783937b0be8ce8b84ea24.poster.avif?t=1741346132\" class=\"bb_img\" width=620 height=124 /></picture></span>「Replik Survivors」 is a time survival game with role-playing and roguelite elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a replik(clone girl) to defeat the Lab's enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/80e4f6bbc5a83cd34c6372de1abc4a0d.poster.avif?t=1741346132\" width=620 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/80e4f6bbc5a83cd34c6372de1abc4a0d.webm?t=1741346132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>In this game, You can use the enhancement system to freely construct various attack triggers, arrange the order, and make your own skill set.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, there are several different characters waiting for you to find out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・A wide selection of attack styles and enhanced attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・7 kinds of characters with completely different playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・5 levels of difficulty, different enemies, different bosses.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on the image above to join the Discord server.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/6daa4738e36783937b0be8ce8b84ea24.apng?t=1741346132\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/6daa4738e36783937b0be8ce8b84ea24.poster.avif?t=1741346132\" class=\"bb_img\" width=620 height=124 /></picture></span>「Replik Survivors」 is a time survival game with role-playing and roguelite elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a replik(clone girl) to defeat the Lab's enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/80e4f6bbc5a83cd34c6372de1abc4a0d.poster.avif?t=1741346132\" width=620 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/80e4f6bbc5a83cd34c6372de1abc4a0d.webm?t=1741346132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>In this game, You can use the enhancement system to freely construct various attack triggers, arrange the order, and make your own skill set.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, there are several different characters waiting for you to find out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・A wide selection of attack styles and enhanced attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・7 kinds of characters with completely different playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・5 levels of difficulty, different enemies, different bosses.</p>",
